/* ===== Agent (MCP) gates ===== */
"OFF by default. Agents can always read metrics and run dry-run previews. With this on, an agent can run a real `mo clean` / `optimize` — but ONLY when it also passes an explicit confirm flag, so a deletion is never one stray sentence away. Turn it off and agents are read-only again. Data stays on this Mac." = "默认关闭。智能体始终可以读取指标并运行预览（dry-run）。开启后，智能体可以真正执行 `mo clean` / `optimize` — 但仅当它同时传入显式的确认参数时才会执行，因此删除绝不会因一句口误而发生。关闭后智能体恢复只读。数据保留在这台 Mac 上。";
